{"tid":650201,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"969四眼司機超好人！你要加油","createTime":"2018-05-02T06:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T09:33:29.000Z","uid":30038,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d76dd87e571cb7eca6722a2128699e6fdae90376","tid":650201,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"今日第一次由銅鑼灣入天水圍要坐969轉967<br />\n咁要永吉街落車轉967，我早一個站落下層準備<br />\n落車啦，就見到司機係度解答緊一位老先生問題<br />\n<br />\n起初我都不以為然，咁我落車之後就搵967個站係邊啦，呢個時候重未開車嘅969司機竟然開左前門問我係咪轉車同叫左我上返車，原來架967岩岩走左，佢幫我追左一個站等我趕到架967（後來睇返原來要廿分鐘一班）<br />\n<br />\n香港地打份工嘅好多都行屍走肉，咁肯幫人同有熱誠嘅司機真係好少有，祝你事業愛情兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs 沿路啲廢老同盲閪亂9過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 短短一個站鉢左45次，老人家唔係大閪晒，祝你地出入平安唔好累到啲司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc14c8d7ebe74d7bfe340e56d508d454fff6d06","tid":650201,"uid":131259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"有D巴士司機係放工時段上哂客之後會教暗D燈比客訓覺"},{"pid":"81157cdb28f96e88f60eeb208ece19fad2090a8a","tid":650201,"uid":30038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"不過講起巴士，狗巴個app食撚左屎咁，人地趕時間果陣想睇下班車幾時到，你就整個廣告重要短片我嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前tg 有bot 可以睇班次，宜家要焗睇廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de586dbdd7a8885e0aa805719f789edb026c3bb1","tid":650201,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc14c8d7ebe74d7bfe340e56d508d454fff6d06","tid":650201,"uid":131259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"有D巴士司機係放工時段上哂客之後會教暗D燈比客訓覺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:31:00.000Z","msg":"呢d